Subject: [PATCH AUTOSEL 5.4 09/24] drm/mipi-dsi: Fix detach call without attach
Date: Mon, 22 Jan 2024 10:16:23 -0500
Message-ID: <20240122151659.997085-9-sashal@kernel.org>
X-Mailer: git-send-email 2.43.0
